This website was created by hand with love and affection on an old but trustworthy gaming laptop. It is written in HTML, Markdown, Nunjucks, CSS, and Javascript.

[Eleventy](https://www.11ty.dev/) is used for static page generation. [Git](https://git-scm.com/) is used for version control. [Github](https://github.com) is used to store the repository. This site is hosted on [Netlify](https://www.netlify.com/).

The primary serif typeface is [Crimson Pro](https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Crimson+Pro). Also used as a secondary serif is the [Bitter](https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Bitter) typeface. The text has a 5:1 contrast ratio at Level AA or better, as specified by [WCAG 2.0](https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG20/).    
    


